k=1,2,3,...,(n-1)
|1-\omega^k|
\sum_1^{n-1}|1-\omega^k|^2=\sum_1^{n-1}(1-2\omega^k +\omega^{2k})=n-1 -2\sum_1^{n-1}\omega^k + \sum_1^{n-1}\omega^{2k}.
