|z|^2=z\cdot\overline{z}
 |1-\omega^k|^2=(1-\omega^k)(1-\overline{\omega}^k)=(1-\omega^k)(1-\omega^{-k}). 
 | 1 - \omega|^2 \neq (1-\omega)^2
|1 - \omega|^2 = |1 - \omega | | 1 - \overline{\omega} | = 1 - (\omega + \overline{\omega}) + \omega \overline{\omega} 
